title: The Baby Huey Story - The Living Legend
description:
incredible and only album from Baby Huey, released 1971, produced by Curtis Mayfield.  This shit is no joke, dead fucking serious, blow yo&#039; mind type of shit.  Listen to the man...  Wu Tang sampled "Hard Times" off this album... includes three tracks not on the original release - Mighty Might Children, Part 1; Hard Times (mono mix); Running (mono mix).

Make your life better.  Listen to THIS.
